{"tid":1880043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用CSI口罩唔拉，搜出多一張八達通就鳩拉，呢個就係亞洲最佳狗賊工作","createTime":"2020-02-14T14:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T19:51:05.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"13795e0cefbbd3d93727e848a88a1c536c6e1a05","tid":1880043,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T14:27:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%A3%E6%92%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8A%E5%91%A8%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%AD%A6-%E7%B5%95%E9%9D%9E%E6%BF%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%90%9C%E5%87%BA%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A-%E6%B6%89%E7%9B%9C%E7%AB%8A%E7%BD%AA%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%2592%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%2591%25A8%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%25B5%2595%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2585%25AB%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%2580%259A-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%259B%259C%25E7%25AB%258A%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%2F&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNhAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=f519ce4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%2592%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%2591%25A8%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E7%25B5%2595%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2585%25AB%25E9%2581%2594%25E9%2580%259A-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E7%259B%259C%25E7%25AB%258A%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%2F&h=175ae2bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E5%BB%A3%E6%92%AD%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E4%B8%8A%E5%91%A8%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%AD%A6-%E7%B5%95%E9%9D%9E%E6%BF%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%90%9C%E5%87%BA%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%85%AB%E9%81%94%E9%80%9A-%E6%B6%89%E7%9B%9C%E7%AB%8A%E7%BD%AA%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95/</a><br />\n<br />\n城市廣播學生記者上周被捕 警：絕非濫捕 搜出長者八達通 涉盜竊罪拘捕<br />\n<br />\n城市大學學生媒體《城市廣播》一名記者在採訪期間於上周六在將軍澳被捕，發表聲明指警方妨礙新聞自由及濫捕記者，<strong>警方今日回應指警員曾截查一名24歲本地男子，並在其身上搜出一張不屬於他的長者八達通，故以「盜竊罪」將其拘捕</strong>，「警察依法辦事，絕非濫捕，涉事人的背景絕非警方執法的考慮因素。」<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，一向尊重新聞自由，並會在不影響行動的大前提下，盡量配合和便利傳媒採訪。就警方於2月9日凌晨時分在將軍澳尚德邨一帶的拘捕行動，警員曾截查一名24歲本地男子，並在其身上搜出一張不屬於他的長者八達通，故以「盜竊罪」將其拘捕。警察依法辦事，絕非濫捕，而涉事人的背景絕非警方執法的考慮因素。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方十分重視聲明中涉及性騷擾的指控，並呼籲涉事人盡快與警方聯絡或作出投訴，提供相關證據，讓警方能夠展開調查，秉公處理。<br />\n<br />\n上周六（8日）是科大學生周梓樂墮樓逝世 3 個月，數百市民在其墮樓現場將軍澳尚德停車場悼念，後來演變成警民衝突，共 119 人被捕，包括 2 名記者及 5 位區議員。城市大學學生媒體《城市廣播》今日發聲明，指一名記者採訪期間被警方以盜竊罪拘捕，扣留 24 小時後獲釋，期間多次受到警員威嚇及性擾攘，稱呼他為「死 gay 閪」，更揚言會雞姦他。"},{"pid":"04da46183be424cd760c14bcb4b243803fe82709","tid":1880043,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:48:53.000Z","msg":"跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNhAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=c2c6e405\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"a1f39e2db629cb938270854ababec7b4c1dacfd7","tid":1880043,"uid":4931,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T17:54:10.000Z","msg":"點解唔帶得長者卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咪證明我用過罰錢囉<br />\n<br />\n垃圾狗"},{"pid":"2eccdf2f7de0bbde386243d307d3eabe36cec63c","tid":1880043,"uid":89683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T19:07:01.000Z","msg":"警城隧轉車站截查15歲仔 檢兩張八達通涉盜竊被捕<br />\n 2019-09-23 09:43香港<br />\n     <br />\n警方昨晚在城門隧道一帶設置路障，於轉車站截查一名15歲少年時，在其錢包內檢獲兩張懷疑屬於他人的八達通卡。<br />\n<br />\n少年涉嫌盜竊被捕，遭警方扣留調查，案件交荃灣警區刑事調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"18c5a5e7844d49149d82917dc1c23a743c795fa8","tid":1880043,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T19:26:05.000Z","msg":"呀豬呀狗都買得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795f659d8304a82872222c891491230fefc54959","tid":1880043,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T19:29:53.000Z","msg":"拉自己咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c8de2c70e38f951472d0a1ca4465d58f7528d9","tid":1880043,"uid":156579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T19:45:16.000Z","msg":"係有罪你就快啲判<br />\n原來香港人只可以有一張八達通<br />\n我自己身上都三張大人卡又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dabcadf59bc38003f7a3365aa37366648ef87124","tid":1880043,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T19:51:05.000Z","msg":"法例唔比藏有長者八達通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}